    <string name="perm_dialog_title">Network &amp; Privacy</string>
    <string name="perm_dialog_msg">KlippShell requires network access to establish a direct interface with your printer\'s Moonraker API. The internet connection is necessary for OTA update checks, providing status assets for the Android TV Launcher, and advanced companion features. Data security is our highest priority: communication occurs exclusively locally between your device and the printer. No control or telemetry data is transmitted to external servers.</string>
